V0240_01_00_00_0.text:
I am Sherry LeBlanc.
I shall test your courage under fire.

V0240_01_00_01_0.text:
You will Duel me.
In fact, our battle has already begun!

V0240_01_00_02_0.text:
This Duel is sort of a meet and greet.
Let us have fun.

V0240_01_00_03_0.text: I am not afraid to take you down.

V0240_01_00_04_0.text:
I am here because I want to be.
Now let us Duel!

V0240_01_00_05_0.text: Since you have to face me, even you know your quest is over.

V0240_01_00_06_0.text: Monsieur Fudo, have you finally decided to join my team?

V0240_01_00_08_0.text:
Z-one...
The one whose power rivals that of the divine...

V0240_01_00_09_0.text:
This isn't a practice session, Elsworth.
It's a real Duel!

V0240_03_00_00_0.text: We feel most alive when we Duel beyond the limits of speed!

V0240_03_00_01_0.text: If I draw a certain card, you are guaranteed to lose!

V0240_03_00_04_0.text: Leaving me with LP is a mistake you should not have made!

V0240_03_00_05_0.text:
You've outmaneuvered me... so far!
But that will not last!

V0240_05_00_00_0.text: How tragic that your successes would lead to your defeat!

V0240_06_01_01_0.text: Just what I was waiting for!

V0240_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0240_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0240_21_00_00_0.text: Even you must realize that victory is impossible!

V0240_21_00_01_1.text: Just because you survived is no cause for celebration.

V0240_21_00_04_0.text: Let's see what surprises you have in store!

V0240_21_00_05_0.text:
Be careful.
I have a strategy that will counteract yours!

V0240_28_00_00_0.text: This Duel may be over, but I see many more in store for us.

V0240_28_00_02_0.text: I am done running from those who dare to threaten me!

V0240_28_00_03_0.text: It's not hard to win when you have something to fight for.

V0240_28_00_04_0.text:
You're a tough opponent.
I hope you never become my enemy.

V0240_28_00_05_0.text: A few turns was all it took to get to know one another.

V0240_28_00_05_1.text:
Your cards told me who you really are.
As did mine for you.

V0240_28_00_06_0.text: I battle on the brink of speed.

V0240_28_00_06_1.text: I sense this is how you'd like to Duel as well.

V0240_28_00_07_0.text:
Haha.
Aren't you an interesting one.

V0240_28_00_08_0.text: Elsworth, you need to sharpen your skills.

V0240_29_00_00_0.text: I had many chances - but failed to execute on any of them.

V0240_29_00_01_0.text:
Magnifique.
You intrigue me more than ever.

V0240_29_00_02_0.text: It must be nice to be so happy after just one victory.

V0240_29_00_03_0.text: Not many can solve my strategies - but you did.

V0240_29_00_04_0.text:
You've caught my attention.
I hope I see you again.

V0240_29_00_05_0.text:
Not even a single good moment...
Maybe next time.

V0240_29_00_06_0.text: What inspires you to Duel the way you do?

V0240_29_00_07_0.text: My father taught me to fight with all my heart, but...

V0240_29_00_11_0.text: Elsworth, I've never seen you so determined to win.

V0240_30_00_00_0.text: If you're intending to Synchro Summon, your card must be...

V0240_30_00_02_0.text: So that's what you were aiming for!

V0240_34_00_00_0.text: I know you're after me so you can steal this card!

V0240_34_00_01_0.text: Where did you get that card!

V0240_34_00_02_0.text: You made me wait this long for such a pitiful maneuver?

V0240_34_00_03_0.text: Being nice to me is a faux pas.

V0240_34_00_04_0.text: Why would you continue a Duel you have no chance of winning?

V0240_34_00_05_0.text: What is wrong with wanting to reunite with my family?

V0240_34_00_06_0.text: You will join no team but my own!

V0240_34_00_07_0.text: Decreasing your LP to destroy my monsters was a mistake.

V0240_34_00_08_0.text: You're driving too fast, even for a Turbo Duel.

V0240_34_00_09_0.text: Only at the edge of speed can you learn about yourself.

V0240_34_00_10_0.text: It's only taken these few turns to learn all about you.

V0240_34_00_12_0.text: Don't lie! I know you're trying to trick me!

V0240_34_00_14_0.text: I will end this quickly, Elsworth.

V0240_35_00_00_0.text:
My name is Sherry LeBlanc.
Ready to Duel?

V0240_36_00_01_0.text: Bring this Duel to an end.

V0240_08_00_00_0.text: This card activates when it's destroyed!

V0240_08_00_00_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Z-ONE's effect from my Graveyard!

V0240_08_00_01_0.text: The card my father left me will be the one that ends you!

V0240_08_00_01_1.text: Z-ONE's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0240_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Ecole de Zone!

V0240_08_00_03_0.text: The Field Spell, Ecole de Zone's effect activates!

V0240_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Fleuret de Fleur!

V0240_08_00_05_0.text: Fleuret de Fleur activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0240_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Synchro Dilemma!

V0240_08_00_07_0.text: I activate my Continuous Spell, Synchro Dilemma's effect!

V0240_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Soul Binding Gate!

V0240_08_00_08_1.text: You will go no further - even if it costs me everything!

V0240_08_00_09_1.text: That monster is destroyed, and we both take damage!

V0240_08_00_10_0.text: No matter what you try, you will not pass through this gate!

V0240_08_00_11_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Imitation!

V0240_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Pennant of Revolution!

V0240_08_00_13_0.text: I activate Pennant of Revolution's effect!

V0240_08_00_14_0.text:
I reveal my Trap Card!
Liberty at Last!!

V0240_08_00_15_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Floral Shield!

V0240_08_00_16_0.text:
I play my Trap Card!
Chain Close!

V0240_08_00_17_0.text: My Trap Card, For Our Dreams!

V0240_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Fleur de Vertiges!

V0240_09_00_00_0.text: Chevalier de Fleur activates her effect!

V0240_09_00_00_1.text: She negates and destroys your Spells and Traps!

V0240_09_00_01_0.text: Chevalier de Fleur can negate your Spells and Traps!

V0240_09_00_02_0.text: I activate Baronne de Fleur's effect!

V0240_09_00_03_0.text: Baronne de Fleur activates her effect!

V0240_09_00_04_0.text: I activate Baronne de Fleur's effect!

V0240_09_00_05_0.text: Sorciere de Fleur activates her effect!

V0240_09_00_06_0.text: I activate Sauge de Fleur's effect!

V0240_09_00_08_0.text: I activate White Steed of the Floral Knights from the Grave!

V0240_09_00_09_0.text: I activate Horse of the Floral Knights's effect!

V0240_09_00_10_0.text: Noble Knight's Shield-Bearer activates its effect!

V0240_09_00_11_0.text: I activate Noble Knight's Spearholder's effect!

V0240_09_00_13_0.text: Necro Fleur activates when it's destroyed by an effect!

V0240_09_00_14_0.text: Fleur Synchron activates when it's used to Synchro Summon!

V0240_09_00_16_0.text: I activate Burgundy the Magic Elf's effect!

V0240_37_00_00_0.text: Arriving faster than the speed of light!

V0240_37_00_00_1.text:
Bringing victory to the palm of my hand!
I Synchro Summon!

V0240_37_00_01_0.text: The noble flower rises for the rebellion!

V0240_37_00_01_1.text:
Bringing victory to the palm of my hand!
I Synchro Summon!

V0240_13_00_01_0.text:
Bloom in glory!
Baronne de Fleur!

V0240_13_00_05_0.text: Here comes White Steed of the Floral Knights!

V0240_13_00_06_0.text: Witness the majesty of Horse of the Floral Knights!

V0240_19_00_05_0.text:
White Steed of the Floral Knights!
Attack!

V0240_19_00_06_0.text: Attack, Horse of the Floral Knights!

V0240_26_00_00_0.text: I see you are here to fight!
